ANTIPHON
-
~From sunset to sunrise
~Everyone in bed lies,
~During all the long night
~Everyone's hiding from light.
~.
~Every date
~tomorrow as today
~Everywhere
~People stopped to care.
~.
~From sunrise to dawn
~Somebody is born
~At least twenty hours
~Men are in their towers.
~.
~Every date
~tomorrow as today
~Everywhere...
~Impossible to bear.
